ils.</p><p> </p><p><strong>9.MODIFICATIONS TO THE PRIVACY POLICY</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">We reserve the right to modify this privacy policy at any time to reflect changes in applicable law, security enhancements or modifications to the functionality of the app. In the event of significant changes, we may notify you through official app store channels. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed of any updates.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"> </p><p><strong>10.CONTACT</strong></p><p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy and the handling and security of your data, please contact our support team using the following information:</p><p><strong>Apprecano Ltd </strong></p><p><strong>Pirkanmaa, Finland </strong></p><p><a href=\"mailto:Info@nelya.app\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Info@nelya.app</strong></a></p>
